title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Luang Prabanng airport
description:
In this addon spotlight we are going to look Luang Prabanng airport which is an airport located in the Northern part of Laos and us used both for international and domestic flights. 
This is the first release of the airport but it already looks pretty promising. Besides the interior of the terminal and tower which is currently missing the airport has got several nice details.

If you want to also add this airport to MSFS 2020 download it via the link below:
https://flightsim.to/file/19516/vllb-luang-prabanng-international-airport
